title: Joaquín Jaunsolo
text:
Joaquín Jaunsolo (born 12 September 1998) is an <a href="Uruguayan%20people">Uruguay</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who generally plays as a <a href="prop%20%28rugby%20union%29">prop</a> represents <a href="Uruguay%20national%20rugby%20union%20team">Uruguay</a> internationally. He was included in the <a href="2019%20Rugby%20World%20Cup%20squads">Uruguayan squad</a> for the <a href="2019%20Rugby%20World%20Cup">2019 Rugby World Cup</a> which was held in Japan for the first time and also marked his first World Cup appearance.
Career.
He made his international debut for Uruguay against Argentina XV on 23 February 2019.
